    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"943998\">JK</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/proof.20by.20induction/near/539412648\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This makes me think that <code>induction n</code> should work(?)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>it works but you get inaccessible variables which are the same as all the other variables but you can't refer to them by name</p>",
